room_title: Escape room "Cuckoo's Clock" by Missing Pieces Escape Games in Minneapolis - St. Paul
room_description: Clara von Clockenstein has unleashed her diabolical genius on the Twin Cities! The mad machinist has been tinkering away at the beloved Minneapolis Clock Tower, and has turned it into a devious device to wipe out the city's technology. Now, only you can stop her villainous plot - and the clock is ticking.
